flowRoot.flowPara: To compensate low self-esteem (object fixation) with this once-received laurel wreath. About as Intelligent as using always the one and same One-Time-Pad

A laurel wreath is a wreath made of branches and leaves of the laurel (latin laurus). The laurel wreath is a symbol and an insignia for a special honor or distinction, for a victory (eg. killing sheeps or christians) or a special success. So to say the special super-duper superman hero
As a bedside carpet, to sweep dirt under the carpet (note this picture represents a faux fur lion, so no animal had to die according to the data of the photographer)

The carnivorous lion symbolizes the Alpha Dog in a "social"-system; A ratio of 1 Alpha Dog to 9 special normal Dogs can make up to 9 times profit with selling such carpets, see "Diner for One" even if it is not directly a lion.
